Items.c: 好啦,你的恩公已經知道錯了,他以後不會再逞強,隨便把腳伸出來送給別人砍了。你就安心回去吧！
Items.mt: Well, your benefactor already knows his mistake, he won't be so brave as to give his foot to someone else to chop. You can go back in peace!
